Component.Description:
A component which allows the entity to be rotated around its yaw axis by the user, or pitched
up and down relative to the user's location.

@param size The size measurement of the entity with which to calculate the yaw rotation.
@param drag How fast the entity rotation decelerates when the user stops manipulating.
@param isGrabbed Used by system to track component state. You should not set this manually, and always use the default value.
@param isSpinning Used by system to track component state. You should not set this manually, and always use the default value.
@param pitch Used by system to track component state. You should not set this manually, and always use the default value.
